description: Number of partitions of n into partition numbers.
references: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
links: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
maple: with(combinat): gf := 1/product((1-q^numbpart(k)), k=1..20): s := series(gf, q, 200): for i from 1 to 199 do printf(`%d,`,coeff(s, q, i)) od: # _James A. Sellers_, Feb 08 2002
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, _Mira Bernstein_
extensions: More terms from _James A. Sellers_, Feb 08 2002
